     Norway How to Contact the Norwegian Consumer Protection Authorities

   The following information will allow you to contact the Norwegian
   consumer protection authorities directly:

   Internet Website:

     www.forbrukerombudet.no (Norwegian Â– also has an English section)

   Telephonic Inquiries:

     + 47 23 400 600

   Fax Inquiries:

     + 47 23 400 601

   E-Mail Inquiries:

     fo@forbrukerombudet.dep.no

   Mailing Address:

     Post Box 4597 Nydalen, 0404 Oslo


